OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FDry but mostly cloudy to
OL,6,Fstart on Tuesday, with some brief
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Patchy cloud with a
OL,8,Frisk of showers into the afternoon and
OL,9,Fevening. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fcloudy start with some light rain or
OL,13,Fshowers Wednesday, brighter later.
OL,14,FBreezy but bright or sunny and largely
OL,15,Fdry Thursday. Dry and sunny Friday.
OL,16,FTemperatures rising, becoming very
OL,17,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
